                {
                    "line_number": 1,
                    "line_text": "Près du laboureur poitrinaire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 2,
                    "line_text": "Devant sa porte, au jour tombant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 3,
                    "line_text": "Est venu s'asseoir sur son banc",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Le patriarche centenaire.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Près du laboureur poitrinaire,\nDevant sa porte, au jour tombant,\nEst venu s'asseoir sur son banc\nLe patriarche centenaire."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Et, comme le gars se désole,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Dit qu'on va bientôt l'enterrer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "L'ancêtre, pour le rassurer,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Lui répond : « T'es jeunʼ, ça m' console.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et, comme le gars se désole,\nDit qu'on va bientôt l'enterrer,\nL'ancêtre, pour le rassurer,\nLui répond : « T'es jeunʼ, ça m' console."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Ton temps est pas vʼnu d' dire adieu",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "À toutʼ les bellʼ choses d'la vie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "L' soleil, l'air, te rʼmettront ; j' me fie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "À ces grands médʼcins du bon Dieu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ton temps est pas vʼnu d' dire adieu\nÀ toutʼ les bellʼ choses d'la vie.\nL' soleil, l'air, te rʼmettront ; j' me fie\nÀ ces grands médʼcins du bon Dieu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "L'hiver, l'arbre est en maladie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "I' n'a plus d'oiseaux ni d' couleurs,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Mais, i' rʼprend ses musiqʼ, ses fleurs :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "C' n'est que d' la nature engourdie.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "L'hiver, l'arbre est en maladie,\nI' n'a plus d'oiseaux ni d' couleurs,\nMais, i' rʼprend ses musiqʼ, ses fleurs :\nC' n'est que d' la nature engourdie."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Et puis, pour les tiens, d' si bravʼ gens,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Qui sont pas avancés d'argent,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Faut q' tu vivʼ ! t' es utile encor.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et puis, pour les tiens, d' si bravʼ gens,\nQui sont pas avancés d'argent,\nFaut q' tu vivʼ ! t' es utile encor."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Tandis q' moi, tant d'âgʼ me suffit.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Maintʼnant, plus à chargʼ qu'à profit,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "J' suis assez vieux pour faire un mort ! »",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Tandis q' moi, tant d'âgʼ me suffit.\nMaintʼnant, plus à chargʼ qu'à profit,\nJ' suis assez vieux pour faire un mort ! »"
        }
    ],
    "corpus": "mel"
